INSERT INTO `wp_posts` VALUES("25", "1", "2011-11-18 10:45:25", "2011-11-18 10:45:25", "[caption id=\"attachment_26\" align=\"alignright\" width=\"210\"]<a href=\"http://www.templatation.com/jsmisc/wp-content/uploads/2013/05/1560453848_3dcbc7a9eb_b1.jpg\"><img class=\"size-medium wp-image-26\" alt=\"Wonderful serenity\" src=\"http://www.templatation.com/jsmisc/wp-content/uploads/2013/05/1560453848_3dcbc7a9eb_b1-210x300.jpg\" width=\"210\" height=\"300\" /></a> Wonderful serenity[/caption]\n\n[dropcap]W[/dropcap]hen, while the lovely valley teems with vapour around me, and the meridian sun strikes the upper surface of the impenetrable foliage of my trees, and but a few stray gleams steal into the inner sanctuary, I throw myself down among the tall grass by the trickling stream; and, as I lie close to the earth, a thousand unknown plants are noticed by me: when I hear the buzz of the little world among the stalks, and grow familiar with the countless indescribable forms of the insects and flies\n\nThen I feel the presence of the Almighty, who formed us in his own image, and the breath of that universal love which bears and sustains us, as it floats around us in an eternity of bliss\n\nAnd then, my friend, when darkness overspreads my eyes, and heaven and earth seem to dwell in my soul and absorb its power, like the form of a beloved mistress, then I often think with longing.\n\nOh, would I could describe these conceptions, could impress upon paper all that is living so full and warm within me, that it might be the mirror of my soul, as my soul is the mirror of the infinite God!", "A wonderful serenity has taken possession of my entire soul", "", "publish", "open", "closed", "", "a-wonderful-serenity-has-taken-possession-of-my-entire-soul", "", "", "2011-11-18 10:45:25", "2011-11-18 10:45:25", "", "0", "http://templatation.com/justshop/layout2/?p=25", "0", "post", "", "0");
INSERT INTO `wp_posts` VALUES("30", "1", "2011-11-24 10:49:49", "2011-11-24 10:49:49", "The bedding was hardly able to cover it and seemed ready to slide off any moment. His many legs, pitifully thin compared with the size of the rest of him, waved about helplessly as he looked.\n[quote style=\"boxed\" float=\"right\"] \"What\'s happened to me?\"[/quote]\nhe thought. It wasn\'t a dream. His room, a proper human room although a little too small, lay peacefully between its four familiar walls.\n\nA collection of textile samples lay spread out on the table - Samsa was a travelling salesman - and above it there hung a picture that he had recently cut out of an illustrated magazine and housed in a nice, gilded frame.\n\nIt showed a lady fitted out with a fur hat and fur boa who sat upright, raising a heavy fur muff that covered the whole of her lower arm towards the viewer. Gregor then turned to look out the window at the dull weather.\n\n[highlight]Drops of rain[/highlight]could be heard hitting the pane, which made him feel quite sad.\n\n\"How about if I sleep a little bit longer and forget all this nonsense\", he thought, but that was something he was unable to do because he was used to sleeping on his right, and in his present state couldn\'t get into that position.", "Doing business like this takes much more effort than doing your own business at home", "", "publish", "open", "closed", "", "doing-business-like-this-takes-much-more-effort-than-doing-your-own-business-at-home", "", "", "2011-11-24 10:49:49", "2011-11-24 10:49:49", "", "0", "http://templatation.com/justshop/layout2/?p=30", "0", "post", "", "0");
INSERT INTO `wp_posts` VALUES("34", "1", "2012-06-05 10:56:05", "2012-06-05 10:56:05", "The copy warned the Little Blind Text, that where it came from it would have been rewritten a thousand times and everything that was left from its origin would be the word \"and\" and the Little Blind Text should turn around and return to its own, safe country.\n\n[caption id=\"attachment_36\" align=\"alignleft\" width=\"300\"]<a href=\"http://www.templatation.com/jsmisc/wp-content/uploads/2013/05/3888356671_981766de0f_b1.jpg\"><img class=\"size-medium wp-image-36\" alt=\"Vokalia and Consonantia\" src=\"http://www.templatation.com/jsmisc/wp-content/uploads/2013/05/3888356671_981766de0f_b1-300x209.jpg\" width=\"300\" height=\"209\" /></a> Vokalia and Consonantia[/caption]\n\nBut nothing the copy said could convince her and so it didnt take long until a few insidious Copy Writers ambushed her, made her drunk with Longe and Parole and dragged her into their agency, where they abused her for their projects again and again. And if she hasnt been rewritten, then they are still using her.\n\nFar far away, behind the word mountains, far from the countries Vokalia and Consonantia, there live the blind texts. Separated they live in Bookmarksgrove right at the coast of the Semantics, a large language ocean. A small river named Duden flows by their place and supplies it with the necessary regelialia.\n\n[unordered_list]<ul>\n<li>One day however a small line of blind text by the name of Lorem Ipsum.\n<li>Place your list items here</li>\n<li>Aliquam tincidunt mauris eu risus.</li>\n<li>Vestibulum auctor dapibus neque.</li>\n</ul>[/unordered_list]\n\nIt is a paradisematic country, in which roasted parts of sentences fly into your mouth. Even the all-powerful Pointing has no control about the blind texts it is an almost unorthographic life One day however a small line of blind text by the name of Lorem Ipsum decided to leave for the far World of Grammar.", "A paradisematic country, where roasted parts of sentences fly", "", "publish", "open", "closed", "", "a-paradisematic-country-where-roasted-parts-of-sentences-fly", "", "", "2012-06-05 10:56:05", "2012-06-05 10:56:05", "", "0", "http://templatation.com/justshop/layout2/?p=34", "0", "post", "", "0");
INSERT INTO `wp_posts` VALUES("41", "1", "2012-06-13 11:06:51", "2012-06-13 11:06:51", "Blowzy red vixens fight for a quick jump. Joaquin Phoenix was gazed by MTV for luck. A wizards job is to vex chumps quickly in fog.\n\n[typography font=\"Lobster\" size=\"24\" size_format=\"px\" color=\"#188f6d\"]Watch \"Jeopardy! \"[/typography]\n\nAlex Trebek\'s fun TV quiz game. Woven silk pyjamas exchanged for blue quartz.\n\n[caption id=\"attachment_45\" align=\"aligncenter\" width=\"300\"]<img class=\"size-medium wp-image-45 \" style=\"border: 0px;margin: 0px\" alt=\"Hibiscus-flowers\" src=\"http://www.templatation.com/jsmisc/wp-content/uploads/2013/05/Hibiscus-flowers1-300x300.jpg\" width=\"300\" height=\"300\" /> We are the \"Hibiscus Flowers\"[/caption]\n[divider_flat]\n\n\nBrawny gods just flocked up to quiz and vex him. Adjusting quiver and bow, [ilink url=\"#\" style=\"note\"]Zompyc[1][/ilink] killed the fox. My faxed joke won a pager in the cable TV quiz show. Amazingly few discotheques provide jukeboxes.", "A very bad quack might jinx zippy fowls", "", "publish", "open", "closed", "", "a-very-bad-quack-might-jinx-zippy-fowls", "", "", "2012-06-13 11:06:51", "2012-06-13 11:06:51", "", "0", "http://templatation.com/justshop/layout2/?p=41", "0", "post", "", "0");
INSERT INTO `wp_posts` VALUES("52", "1", "2013-03-14 11:12:58", "2013-03-14 11:12:58", "No one rejects, dislikes, or avoids pleasure itself, because it is pleasure, but because those who do not know how to pursue pleasure rationally encounter consequences that are extremely painful.\n\n[toggle title_open=\"Close Me\" title_closed=\"Open Me\" hide=\"yes\" border=\"yes\" style=\"default\" excerpt_length=\"0\" read_more_text=\"Read More\" read_less_text=\"Read Less\" include_excerpt_html=\"no\"]Nor again is there anyone who loves or pursues or desires to obtain pain of itself, because it is pain, but because occasionally circumstances occur in which toil and pain can procure him some great pleasure.[/toggle]\n\nTo take a trivial example, which of us ever undertakes laborious physical exercise, except to obtain some advantage from it?\n\nBut who has any right to find fault with a man who chooses to enjoy a pleasure that has no annoying consequences, or one who avoids a pain that produces no resultant pleasure?\n\n[box type=\"tick\" size=\"medium\" style=\"rounded\"]Pellentesque habitant morbi tristique senectus et netus et malesuada fames ac turpis egestas. Vestibulum tortor quam, feugiat vitae, ultricies eget, tempor sit amet, ante.[/box]\n\nOn the other hand, we denounce with righteous indignation and dislike men who are so beguiled and demoralized by the charms of pleasure of the moment, so blinded by desire, that they cannot foresee the pain and trouble that are bound to ensue; and equal blame belongs to those who fail in their duty through weakness of will, which is the same as saying through shrinking from toil and pain.", "These cases are perfectly simple and easy to distinguish", "", "publish", "open", "closed", "", "these-cases-are-perfectly-simple-and-easy-to-distinguish", "", "", "2013-03-14 11:12:58", "2013-03-14 11:12:58", "", "0", "http://templatation.com/justshop/layout2/?p=52", "0", "post", "", "0");
